SISTER CATHERINE:
Jordan Adler.

1:35:57.926 --> 1:35:59.623
[CHEERING]

1:35:59.666 --> 1:36:01.016
Congratulations.

1:36:01.059 --> 1:36:02.321
Lisa Alliser.

1:36:02.365 --> 1:36:03.758
[CHEERING CONTINUES]

1:36:07.892 --> 1:36:09.807
Monica Atkinson.

1:36:11.548 --> 1:36:12.854
Oh, my God.

1:36:19.512 --> 1:36:22.080
What are you doing?

1:36:22.124 --> 1:36:23.603
I'm graduating.

1:36:29.827 --> 1:36:31.873
Thank you.

