Um...

1:36:33.875 --> 1:36:35.833
Um, I'm sorry
but there's one other essay

1:36:35.877 --> 1:36:37.139
that's been scheduled

1:36:37.182 --> 1:36:38.401
to be read.

1:36:39.968 --> 1:36:42.666
Okay, that was a bold move.

