[INDISTINCT WHISPERING]

1:36:45.669 --> 1:36:47.236
ADAM'S DARKNESS: Adam.

1:36:49.412 --> 1:36:50.717
Adam...

1:36:50.761 --> 1:36:52.284
[ECHOING AND DISTORTION]

1:36:53.851 --> 1:36:57.289
